# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# TinyAgents .gitignore
#
# Scope: TinyAgents is an AI-Agent SDLC learning project. The repo tracks
# source code, docs, goal specs, helper scripts, and *learning evidence*
# (selected loop markdown). It does NOT track runtime artifacts, generated
# target projects, dependency caches, or environment-specific noise.
#
# See docs/repository-hygiene.md for the rationale.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# --- OS / editor noise ---
.DS_Store
.idea/
.vscode/

# --- Python ---
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
*.egg-info/

# --- Node / Next / build outputs ---
node_modules/
.next/
dist/
build/
coverage/

# --- Environment / secrets ---
.env
.env.*
*.log

# --- Playwright / browser test artifacts ---
.playwright/
playwright-report/
test-results/

# --- TinyAgents runtime artifacts ---
# Per-loop screenshots, build logs, lint logs, etc. are large and
# regenerated on every run; loop markdown (research.md, plan.md,
# test-report.md, review-report.md, next-loop.md) stays tracked.
loops/*/artifacts/
loops/**/artifacts/
loops/**/screenshots/

# --- Generated target projects ---
# Target projects (e.g. portfolio-site) should live in their own repo, not
# inside this learning repo. Ignored at any depth.
portfolio-site/
../portfolio-site/
